Sure, here are some example sentences that use the Serbian word "istovremeno":

1. Istovremeno sam slušala muziku i čitala knjigu. (*Istovremeno* - adverb) (I was listening to music and reading a book at the same time.)

2. Istovremeno sa saobraćajem, grad se razvijao i širio. (*Istovremeno* - adverb) (The city was developing and expanding simultaneously with traffic.)

3. Oni su *istovremeno* bili i prijatelji i poslovni partneri. (*istovremeno* - adverb) (They were both friends and business partners at the same time.)

4. *Istovremeno* sa potpisivanjem ugovora, sprovedena je i isplata. (*Istovremeno* - preposition) (The payment was made simultaneously with the signing of the contract.)

5. U tom trenutku sam se osećala *istovremeno* umorno i uzbuđeno. (*istovremeno* - adverb) (At that moment, I felt both tired and excited at the same time.)

6. *Istovremenošću* ovih procesa postiže se veća efikasnost. (*Istovremenošću* - noun) (The simultaneity of these processes achieves greater efficiency.)

7. Ova situacija je vrlo *istovremena* i kompleksna. (*istovremena* - adjective) (This situation is very simultaneous and complex.)

I hope these examples help!